User Story 1: Viewing Library Rules
As a student,
I want to view library policies and guidelines,
So that I can follow the rules properly.
Acceptance Criteria:
* Given that I navigate to the library info section,
* When I open the policies page,
* Then I should see the library rules.
 
User Story 2: Booking Study Rooms
As a student,
I want to book a study room in the library,
So that I can study with my group in a quiet space.
Acceptance Criteria:
* Given that a study room is available,
* When I submit a booking request,
* Then the system should confirm my reservation.
